      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen excels in driving dynamics, equipped with a factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock and Electronic Damping Control (EDC) for precise lateral load management. The engine's individual throttle bodies provide exceptional response, while the rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014critical maintenance items for this platform\u2014have been proactively addressed. The chassis remains taut with healthy bushings and a subframe free of structural fatigue. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain and hydraulic steering rack offer the visceral feedback sought by purists. A robust example of the final naturally aspirated M-car.",
